Lung transplantation and gender effects on survival of recipients with cystic 
fibrosis.

Raghavan D(1), Gao A(2), Ahn C(2), Kaza V(3), Finklea J(3), Torres F(3), Jain 
R(4).

Author information:
(1)Division of Pulmonary and Critical Care, Central Arkansas Veterans Health 
